  "content": "<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"elev/20150629elev2.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:95%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Wamsutter, WY appears to exist as a support station for the oil and gas industry and an exit on route 80.\n\t\t\t\t\t\tIt was an important place for TD riders since it had all services in the middle of the Wyoming Great Basin.\n\t\t\t\t\t\tLeaving town and going south there were many trucks building, widening or maintaining the gravel road. They\n\t\t\t\t\t\twere also bringing equipment to the well sites. For almost 50 miles until I was close to the Little Snake\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRiver there were wells or stations every 1/2 mile.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"section-heading\">Great Basin</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"carousel1\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"0\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"2\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"3\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-inner\" role=\"listbox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item active\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic0101.JPG\" alt=\"First slide image\"\n                                                          class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Morning in the desert</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Looking south toward Colorado</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic0102.JPG\" alt=\"Second slide image\"\n                                                   class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Morning in the desert</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>East</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic0103.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                   class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Morning in the desert</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>West</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic0104.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                   class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Morning in the desert</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The way I had come</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"left carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel1\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"prev\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"right carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel1\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"next\">\n                                        <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                                        </span><span class=\"sr-only\">Next</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.container carousel 1-->\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t360 view\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"carousel2\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel2\" data-slide-to=\"0\" class=\"active\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel2\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel2\" data-slide-to=\"2\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel2\" data-slide-to=\"3\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-inner\" role=\"listbox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item active\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic0201.JPG\" alt=\"First slide image\"\n                                                                  class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Late morning in the desert</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Looking back the way I had come</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic0202.JPG\" alt=\"Second slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Late morning in the desert</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Looking west</p>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic0203.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Late morning in the desert</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Looking south to where I was going</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic0204.JPG\" alt=\"Forth slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Late morning in the desert</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Looking east</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"left carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel2\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"prev\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"right carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel2\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"next\">\n                                        <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                                        </span><span class=\"sr-only\">Next</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.row -->\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.container carousel 2-->\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"section-heading\">Getting closer to the Colorado mountains </h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"carousel3\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel3\" data-slide-to=\"0\" class=\"active\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel3\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel3\" data-slide-to=\"2\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel3\" data-slide-to=\"3\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-inner\" role=\"listbox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item active\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic031.JPG\" alt=\"First slide image\"\n                                                                  class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Afternoon in the desert</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>1</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic032.JPG\" alt=\"Second slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Afternoon in the desert</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Heading toward these mountains</p>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic033.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Afternoon in the desert</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>3</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic034.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Afternoon in the desert</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>4</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"left carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel3\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"prev\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"right carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel3\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"next\">\n                                        <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                                        </span><span class=\"sr-only\">Next</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.row -->\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.container carousel 3-->\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>The ride had two reasonable hills in the mid-afternoon. After climbing up from 6,600 to 7,700 ft the road\n\t\t\t\t\t\tflattened out for 6 miles or so then went screaming downhill for 3 miles. I was tricked into thinking I'd be\n\t\t\t\t\t\tcoasting into the border area by Slater. The road had a number of turns in it so you couldn't always see\n\t\t\t\t\t\twhat was coming. Before the border Wyoming threw one more hill at me. It was only about a 10 minute hike up\n\t\t\t\t\t\tthis 500 foot hill but I was just not anticipated it at this stage of the day. I knew I had some mountains\n\t\t\t\t\t\tto climb once I got into Colorado so this one caught me by surprise. From the top of that hill it was\n\t\t\t\t\t\tanother steep downhill to the Little Snake River museum.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-12 blog-post\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-8\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.littlesnakerivermuseum.com/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic04.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"95%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span href=\"http://www.littlesnakerivermuseum.com/\" class=\"caption text-muted\">Savery, WY - five miles to Colorado border\n                                    </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-4\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The women who ran the museum sent me down to the basement to help myself to various items in the\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tfridge. I had a couple yogurts and at least 4 cheese sticks to go with 2 cans of Coke. Their break room\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\twas air conditioned so I stayed for a while.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"section-heading\">Colorado = Green - 12 miles up Slater Creek</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic05.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"95%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">I went through a canyon at the bottom of Slater Creek\n                                    </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tThe first 5 miles along Slater Creek was a gradual climb. The surroundings were nice and green again.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic06.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"80%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">Looking back down Slater Creek\n                            </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tLots of ups and down on the way to Brush Mountain Lodge.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic07.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"90%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">It was hard to get a sense of how bad this was going to be\n                            </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tAn hour to go before I rested\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-12 blog-post\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic08.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" class=\"caption text-muted\">back\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic09.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" class=\"caption text-muted\">forward\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"section-heading\">Brush Mountain Lodge</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>The lodge was hidden from the road as I approached. There was another house up higher on the hill behind\n\t\t\t\t\t\tthe lodge that peaked out just before this. This was a fakeout. Once I came around the corner I was really\n\t\t\t\t\t\texcited to know my riding was thru for the day.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic13.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tThis was a day I had looked forward to the entire trip up until now.\n\t\t\t\t\t\tI didn't need to worry about tomorrow I had survived this beast of a ride through my birthday.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic10.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBefore I could sit down I had been offered Lemonade and Cheeseburgers for my belly and ice for my knees.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-12 blog-post\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic11.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" class=\"caption text-muted\">At last\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic12.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" class=\"caption text-muted\">Would you like some ice with your Lemonade?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Eric had arrived before me. Tom, Lynne and Rob arrived shortly after and Andrew was the last to arrive. I\n\t\t\t\t\t\thad ridden in the vicinity of these riders since before entering Wyoming.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-12 blog-post\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic14.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">Big crowd at Brush Mountain\n                                    </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day21/day21pic15.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">Andrew\n                                    </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tDay 21 - Monday, June 29 - 82 miles - Wamsutter, WY to Brush Mountain Lodge\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Text by <a href=\"http://www.havingadventures.com/\">Jim O'Brien</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t. Photographs by Jim O'Brien<a href=\"https://flic.kr/s/aHsk9CwBC1\">TD on Flickr</a>.</p>"
}